plex cataract surgery with premium intra- ocular lenses and other anterior segment surgeries. She has a warm demeanor and a friendly personality.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;',1,11,'Services',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,_binary '','2024-07-31 07:47:23','2024-07-31 07:48:26','1722412043.jpg'),(68,'&lt;p&gt;xczxczxcxcxcvxcvxcxv&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;xczx&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;xc&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;cxcxxx&lt;img src=&quot;../../storage/uploads/QDsnq7DI8TMpYrB5YrnOdOAZeMsYQCrSI8IEWjeH.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;147&quot; height=&quot;122&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',1,12,'sercv',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,_binary '','2024-07-31 12:35:54','2024-07-31 12:46:23','1722429354.png');
